    dcterms:title "Judgment of the Court (First Chamber) of 11 December 2008.#Commission of the European Communities v Département du Loiret and Scott SA.#Appeal - State aid - Preferential price of a plot of land - Commission decision - Recovery of aid incompatible with the common market - Present-day value of the aid - Compound interest rate - No statement of reasons - Complete annulment - Lawfulness.#Case C-295/07 P."@en .

<https://e.cjeu.europa.eu/judgment/ECLI:EU:C:2008:723> a eli:LegalResource ;
