    dcterms:title "Judgment of the Court (First Chamber) of 3 September 2009.#William Prym GmbH & Co. KG and Prym Consumer GmbH & Co. KG v Commission of the European Communities.#Appeal - Competition - Agreements, decisions and concerted practices - European haberdashery market (needles) - Market sharing agreements - Infringement of the rights of the defence - Obligation to state the reasons on which the decision is based - Fine - Guidelines - Gravity of the infringement - Actual impact on the market - Implementation of the cartel.#Case C-534/07 P."@en .

