<https://e.cjeu.europa.eu/judgment/ECLI:EU:C:2009:719> a eli:LegalResource ;
    eli:id_local "62008CJ0314" ;
    eli:number "314/08" ;
    dcterms:identifier "ECLI:EU:C:2009:719" ;
    dcterms:title "Judgment of the Court (Third Chamber) of 19 November 2009.#Krzysztof Filipiak v Dyrektor Izby Skarbowej w Poznaniu.#Reference for a preliminary ruling: Wojewódzki Sąd Administracyjny w Poznaniu - Poland.#Income tax legislation - Right to deduct social security contributions from the basis of assessment for tax - Right to a tax reduction on the basis of health insurance contributions paid - Refusal where contributions are paid in a Member State other than the State of taxation - Whether compatible with Articles 43 EC and 49 EC - Judgment of the national constitutional court - Unconstitutionality of provisions of national law - Deferral of the date on which those provisions are to lose their binding force - Primacy of Community law - Implications for the national court.#Case C-314/08."@en .

<https://e.cjeu.europa.eu/judgment/ECLI:EU:C:2009:742> a eli:LegalResource ;
