    dcterms:title "Judgment of the Court (Fifth Chamber) of 16 June 2022.#Port de Bruxelles and Région de Bruxelles-Capitale v Infrabel SA.#Request for a preliminary ruling from the Cour d'appel de Bruxelles.#Reference for a preliminary ruling – Trans-European transport network – Regulation (EU) No 1315/2013 – Article 15(1) – Inland waterways transport infrastructure – Inland ports – Obligation of a Member State to connect inland ports with road or rail transport infrastructure – Removal of the connection with one of those two types of transport infrastructure – Conditions.#Case C-229/21."@en .

