    dcterms:identifier "ECLI:EU:C:2022:639" ;
    dcterms:title "Judgment of the Court (Grand Chamber) of 7 September 2022.#E.K. v Staatssecretaris van Justitie en Veiligheid.#Request for a preliminary ruling from the Rechtbank Den Haag, zittingsplaats Amsterdam.#Reference for a preliminary ruling – Directive 2003/109/EC – Status of third-country nationals who are long-term residents – Scope – Third-country national with a right of residence under Article 20 TFEU – Article 3(2)(e) – Residence solely on temporary grounds – Autonomous concept of EU law.#Case C-624/20."@en .

