    dcterms:title "Judgment of the Court (Second Chamber) of 16 July 2015.#ClientEarth and Pesticide Action Network Europe (PAN Europe) v European Food Safety Authority.#Appeal — Access to documents of the institutions of the European Union — Regulation (EC) No 1049/2001 — Article 4(1)(b) — Regulation (EC) No 45/2001 — Article 8 — Exception to right of access — Protection of personal data — Concept of ‘Personal data’ — Conditions for transfer of personal data — Names of authors of each comment on European Food Safety Authority (EFSA) draft guidance relating to scientific documents to be included in applications for authorisation to place plant protection products on the market — Refusal of access.#Case C-615/13 P."@en .

