    dcterms:title "Judgment of the Court (Grand Chamber) of 18 December 2007.#Kingdom of Sweden v Commission of the European Communities and Others.#Appeal - Regulation (EC) No 1049/2001 - Public access to documents of the institutions - Documents originating from a Member State - Objection of the Member State to disclosure of the documents - Scope of Article 4(5) of the regulation.#Case C-64/05 P."@en .

