    dcterms:title "Judgment of the Court (Grand Chamber), 16 October 2012.#European Commission v Republic of Austria.#Failure of a Member State to fulfil obligations – Directive 95/46/EC – Processing of personal data and free movement of such data – Protection of natural persons – Article 28(1) – National supervisory authority – Independence – Supervisory authority and the Federal Chancellery – Personal and organisational links.#Case C‑614/10."@en .

