    dcterms:title "Judgment of the Court (Third Chamber) of 5 May 2011.#Deutsche Telekom AG v Bundesrepublik Deutschland.#Reference for a preliminary ruling: Bundesverwaltungsgericht - Germany.#Electronic communications - Directive 2002/22/EC - Article 25(2) - Directive 2002/58/EC - Article 12 - Provision of directory enquiry services and directories - Obligation placed on an undertaking assigning telephone numbers to pass to other undertakings data in its possession relating to the subscribers of third-party undertakings.#Case C-543/09."@en .

