    dcterms:title "Judgment of the Court (Second Chamber) of 20 December 2017.#Peter Nowak v Data Protection Commissioner.#Reference for a preliminary ruling — Protection of individuals with regard to the processing of personal data — Directive 95/46/EC — Article 2(a) — Concept of ‘personal data’ — Written answers submitted by a candidate in a professional examination — Examiner’s comments with respect to those answers — Article 12(a) and (b) — Extent of the data subject’s rights to access and rectification.#Case C-434/16."@en,
        "Judgment of the Court (Second Chamber) of 20 December 2017.#Peter Nowak v Data Protection Commissioner.#Request for a preliminary ruling from the Supreme Court.#Reference for a preliminary ruling — Protection of individuals with regard to the processing of personal data — Directive 95/46/EC — Article 2(a) — Concept of ‘personal data’ — Written answers submitted by a candidate in a professional examination — Examiner’s comments with respect to those answers — Article 12(a) and (b) — Extent of the data subject’s rights to access and rectification.#Case C-434/16."@en .

