    dcterms:title "Judgment of the General Court (Sixth Chamber) of 3 December 2015.#CN v European Parliament.#Non-contractual liability — Petition addressed to the Parliament — Dissemination of certain personal data on the Parliament’s website — Absence of a sufficiently serious breach of a rule of law conferring rights on individuals.#Case T-343/13."@en .

