    dcterms:title "Judgment of the Court (Grand Chamber) of 10 July 2018.#Proceedings brought by Tietosuojavaltuutettu.#Request for a preliminary ruling from the Korkein hallinto-oikeus.#Reference for a preliminary ruling — Protection of individuals with regard to the processing of personal data — Directive 95/46/EC — Scope of the directive — Article 3 — Data collected and processed by the members of a religious community in the course of their door-to-door preaching — Article 2(c) — Definition of a ‘personal data filing system’ — Article 2(d) — Definition of a ‘controller’ of the processing of personal data — Article 10(1) of the Charter of Fundamental Rights of the European Union.#Case C-25/17."@en .

