    dcterms:title "Judgment of the Court (Eighth Chamber) of 25 February 2021.#European Commission v Kingdom of Spain.#Failure of a Member State to fulfil obligations – Article 258 TFEU – Directive (EU) 2016/680 – Processing of personal data – Prevention, investigation, detection or prosecution of criminal offences – Failure to transpose and notify the transposition measures – Article 260(3) TFEU – Application for the imposition of a lump sum and a penalty payment.#Case C-658/19."@en .

